 <reference xml:id="ref.pspell" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
  <title>Pspell Functions</title>
  <titleabbrev>Pspell</titleabbrev>

  <partintro>
   <simpara>
    The <function>pspell</function> functions allow you to check the
    spelling of a word and offer suggestions.
   </simpara>
   <simpara>
    You need the aspell and pspell libraries, available from <link
    xlink:href="&url.aspell;">&url.aspell;</link> and
    <link xlink:href="&url.pspell;">&url.pspell;</link> respectively, and
    add the <option role="configure">--with-pspell[=dir]</option> option
    when compiling php.
   </simpara>
  </partintro>

&reference.pspell.entities.functions;

 </reference>
